{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-46","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 46","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete koristiti radio dugmad za pitanja u kojima želite samo jedan odgovor od više opcija.</p>\n<p>Evo primera radio dugmeta sa tekstom <code>cat</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;input type=\"radio\"> cat\n</code></pre>\n<p>Zapamti da je element <code>input</code> prazan element.</p>\n<p>Pre polja za unos teksta, dodajte radio dugme sa tekstom postavljenim kao:</p>\n<p><code>Indoor</code></p>\n</section>","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804dc","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-46"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n \n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[36,39],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da kreirate element <code>input</code> za vaše radio dugme. Proverite sintaksu.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('form > input').length >= 2);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš element <code>input</code> treba da ima otvarajući tag, ali ne i zatvarajući tag.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('form > input') && !code.match(/<\\/input\\>/g));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da dodaš samo jedan element <code>input</code> na tvoj radio dugme. Ukloni sve suvišnosti.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('form > input'), 2);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj novi element <code>input</code> treba da bude iznad postojećeg elementa <code>input</code> čiji je atribut <code>type</code> postavljen na <code>text</code>. Postavio si ih pogrešnim redosledom.</p>","testString":"const existingInputElem = document.querySelector('form > input[type=\"text\"]');\nassert(\n  existingInputElem &&\n    existingInputElem.previousElementSibling.nodeName === 'INPUT'\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoja nova karakteristika <code>input</code> nema atribut <code>type</code>. Proveri da postoji razmak nakon imena oznake za otvaranje.</p>","testString":"assert.isTrue(document.querySelector('input')?.hasAttribute('type'));"},{"text":"<p>Vaša nova funkcija za <code>input</code> treba da ima samo jednu karakteristiku od <code>type</code>. Uklonite sve dodatke.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelector('input')\n  ?.getAttributeNames()\n  .filter(attr => attr === 'type')\n  .length === 1\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj novi element <code>input</code> treba da ima atribut <code>type</code> sa vrednošću <code>radio</code>. Vrednost nedostaje ili je pogrešno napisana. Zapamti da vrednosti atributa treba da budu pod navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\n  document.querySelector('input')?.getAttribute('type'),\n  /^radio$/i\n);"},{"text":"<p>Iako ste postavili atribut <code>input</code> novog elementa <code>type</code> na <code>radio</code>, savetuje se da uvek obuhvatite vrednost atributa navodnicima.</p>","testString":"assert(!/\\<\\s*input\\s+type\\s*=\\s*radio/i.test(code));"},{"text":"<p>Tekst dugmeta <code>radio</code> za/od <code> Indoor</code> treba da bude postavljen posle njega umesto pre njega.</p>","testString":"const radioInputElem = document.querySelector('input');\nassert.notMatch(radioInputElem?.previousSibling?.nodeValue, /Indoor/i);"},{"text":"<p>Tekst <code> Indoor</code> treba da bude smešten direktno desno od vašeg dugmeta <code>radio</code>. Ostavili ste tekst ili postoje greške u pravopisu.</p>","testString":"const radioInputElem = document.querySelector('input');\nassert.match(radioInputElem?.nextSibling?.nodeValue?.replace(/\\s+/g, ' '), /\\s*Indoor/i);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","dashedName":"step-46","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-47","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-45","id":"5ef9b03c81a63668521804dc","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>CatPhotoApp</title>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CatPhotoApp</h1>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Photos</h2>\n        <p>Everyone loves <a href=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\">cute cats</a> online!</p>\n        <p>See more <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\">cat photos</a> in our gallery.</p>\n        <a href=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Lists</h2>\n        <h3>Things cats love:</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>catnip</li>\n          <li>laser pointers</li>\n          <li>lasagna</li>\n        </ul>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/lasagna.jpg\" alt=\"A slice of lasagna on a plate.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <em>love</em> lasagna.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n        <h3>Top 3 things cats hate:</h3>\n        <ol>\n          <li>flea treatment</li>\n          <li>thunder</li>\n          <li>other cats</li>\n        </ol>\n        <figure>\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/cats.jpg\" alt=\"Two tabby kittens sleeping together on a couch.\">\n          <figcaption>Cats <strong>hate</strong> other cats.</figcaption>  \n        </figure>\n      </section>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Cat Form</h2>\n        <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>Is your cat an indoor or outdoor cat?</legend>\n            <label><input id=\"indoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"indoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n            <label><input id=\"outdoor\" type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" value=\"outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <fieldset>\n            <legend>What's your cat's personality?</legend>\n            <label for=\"loving\"><input id=\"loving\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"loving\" checked> Loving</label>\n            <label for=\"lazy\"><input id=\"lazy\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"lazy\"> Lazy</label>\n            <label for=\"energetic\"><input id=\"energetic\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" value=\"energetic\"> Energetic</label>\n          </fieldset>\n          <input type=\"text\" name=\"catphotourl\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n          <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n        </form>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n    <footer>\n      <p>\n        No Copyright - <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org\">freeCodeCamp.org</a>\n      </p>\n    </footer>\n  </body>\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-html-by-building-a-cat-photo-app/step-46"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}